{"tid":1261250,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《罷免韓國瑜30行動》正式啟動      2大超商輸入代碼就能拿到罷免連署書","createTime":"2019-06-27T06:44:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T07:00:28.000Z","uid":35790,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5c4be2fc4239a68b89b407903b771c58773b3ccf","tid":1261250,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T06:44:06.000Z","msg":"《罷韓30行動》正式啟動 2大超商就搞定<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/VaO9BvX\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FVaO9BvX&h=13ff35d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《罷韓30行動》正式啟動，兩大超商輸入代碼就能拿到罷免連署書。（記者黃佳琳翻攝）<br />\n<br />\n「Wecare高雄」號召高雄市民，一起加入罷免高雄市長韓國瑜的行列，為了方便參與的市民能用最便捷的方式取得罷免書，「Wecare高雄」團隊向統一和全家2大超商申請雲端列印代碼，民眾只要到超商使用機台，就可列印到罷免書，填妥後寄到指定郵政信箱，即可完成連署罷免。<br />\n<br />\n「Wecare高雄」團隊指出，7-11的雲端列印代碼為「6805614040」、全家雲端列印代碼為「9225945868」，兩家超商的代碼至6月30日上午11點前有效，若太多機台同時使用同一代碼，機台可能會讀不出檔案，建議過陣子再試，團隊也會持續更新代碼。<br />\n<br />\n民眾列印完罷免書後，可根據書面背面的教學，折三折後用 膠帶封口（多份可單面列印，裝在同一信封），然後購買郵票貼好郵票，找到郵筒或郵局寄出。（平信8元，現時15元），量連署請裝於同一信封，寄送至「80088新興郵局第72號信箱 《罷韓30行動》收」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/m.ltn.com.tw/amp/news/politics/breakingnews/2835177\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Famp%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2835177&d=F8rBtbRGk5TlA8%2FYPnv0doHZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=11b6120c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/m.ltn.com.tw/amp/news/politics/breakingnews/2835177</a>"},{"pid":"bbc73b3a0f758b8a9abdd5016437b7a76077fcc1","tid":1261250,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T06:45:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f88707d0a64a0a5f44e162f79fc1b0e92413f39c","tid":1261250,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T06:45:27.000Z","msg":"罷免林鄭30行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22bdbb1e3e12fc7172157a1569442f20e0e026a4","tid":1261250,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T07:00:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}